SubjectBy-elections (2) - Sturgeon River–Parkland- Lac-Saint-Jean
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of Sturgeon River–Parkland and Lac-Saint-Jean, with polling to take place on October 23, 2017.
